{"tid":2403093,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球王美斯技能，打對手倒地，對手被罰黃牌","createTime":"2021-02-11T01:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T23:49:28.000Z","uid":173952,"like":39,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fbab4f5a0d7a71b102454741d17a95cc55a785","tid":2403093,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sports/transform/26/w518h308/20210211/3cea-kiweitw3194993.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F26%2Fw518h308%2F20210211%2F3cea-kiweitw3194993.gif&h=6d071636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9kv5ub.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9kv5ub.jpg&h=a9546bbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  那是比賽的第62分鐘，西維爾1比0領先，球證拉奧斯判罰霍爾丹對美斯犯規，西維爾方面表示了抗議。當時霍爾丹拿住了皮球，不讓巴塞方面快速開球，美斯對此十分不滿，多個角度的畫面都顯示，美斯從身後去搶皮球時，揚起的手臂打到了對方的臉。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">  霍爾丹倒地，不過球證拉奧斯給了霍爾丹一張黃牌。拉奧斯當時就在事發現場附近，然而不管是他還是VAR，都沒判罰美斯犯規。</span><br />\n<br />\n  在社交網站上，托馬斯&middot;隆塞羅對此表示了不滿：「美斯的肘擊不被處罰，而被他侵犯的人反而吃到了黃牌。這就是利安法則。大家都閉嘴吧。」"},{"pid":"f4054bb2697cf7ddff43f7ecb0f065feb5d18d45","tid":2403093,"uid":159653,"like":11,"dislike":14,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"支那何求技能：跳樓自殺未遂，美斯變出氣袋"},{"pid":"09f12d929579cdf793b8a62c12cec96568322518","tid":2403093,"uid":159653,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"f4054bb2697cf7ddff43f7ecb0f065feb5d18d45","tid":2403093,"uid":159653,"like":11,"dislike":14,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"支那何求技能：跳樓自殺未遂，美斯變出氣袋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:50:54.000Z","msg":"樓主谷撚住唔出聲 等我開多兩個post屌下美斯出下氣先"},{"pid":"4f4b6414edb8dcc31c035fe244aac7e33ab67da1","tid":2403093,"uid":173952,"like":14,"dislike":6,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:53:06.000Z","msg":"疤狗連黑哨都輸波<br />\n係咪代表政府連黑警都將會輸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}